  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00001",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "二童儿、王莽同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00002",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "王莽"
      ],
      "text": "想当年在朝中暗下毒手，一心想篡夺那汉室龙楼。都只为癸亥年中秋节候，孝平帝寿诞日共庆千秋。那时我进了那三杯毒酒，害得他晏了驾我方称心头。实指望坐江山长年远久，又谁知天不佑难以到头。到而今出了个妖人刘秀，统领着人和马要报冤仇。无奈何我藏在云台观口，我只想悟参禅来把道修。",
      "text_length": 133
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00003",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王莽"
      ],
      "text": "孤家王莽。想当年八月中秋，曾用毒药酒害死孝平皇帝，篡夺汉室江山一十八载。实指望汉家绝了后代，不料白水村中，又出了妖人刘秀，招兵聚将，要与平帝报仇。孤家看事不好，来在云台观内参禅悟道，不修今生，也要修修孤的来世吓。",
      "text_length": 106
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00004",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "王莽"
      ],
      "text": "悔当初设毒计害了汉统，哪知道暗地里神鬼不容。善恶事到头来终有报应，镜中花水中月一场空。",
      "text_length": 43
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00005",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "姚期、马武、杜茂、岑彭、邳彤同上。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00006",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期",
        "马武",
        "杜茂",
        "岑彭",
        "邳彤"
      ],
      "text": "来此已是云台，待我等进去，参拜莽主。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00007",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马武"
      ],
      "text": "姚仁兄，你看他等进得观去，你我就在观外稍坐，听他们讲些什么。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00008",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "好，请坐。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00009",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "杜茂、岑彭、邳彤同跪。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00010",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜茂",
        "岑彭",
        "邳彤"
      ],
      "text": "参见莽主。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00011",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王莽"
      ],
      "text": "下面跪的何人？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00012",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜茂"
      ],
      "text": "臣杜茂。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00013",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王莽"
      ],
      "text": "你前来作甚？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00014",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜茂"
      ],
      "text": "迎接莽主。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00015",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王莽"
      ],
      "text": "你哪里说的是什么“迎接”二字，分明是前来捉拿孤家。杜茂吓，杜茂！想当年孤家因你武艺超群，人才出众，曾将大队人马，交付你执掌，你就该一秉忠心扶保孤家，才是正理。怎么你听信那妖道邓禹的谣言，私自带兵投降刘秀，贪图富贵，负义忘恩，反敢前来拿我。有道是：飞鸟尽，良弓藏；狡兔死，走狗烹；敌国破，谋臣亡吓！",
      "text_length": 148
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00016",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "王莽"
      ],
      "text": "见杜茂把我的牙关咬坏，叫一声无义人细听开怀：想孤家相待你恩情似海，到如今降他人所为何来？",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00017",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王莽"
      ],
      "text": "你是何人？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00018",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "岑彭"
      ],
      "text": "臣岑彭见驾。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00019",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王莽"
      ],
      "text": "岑彭，你也是前来捉拿孤家的么？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00020",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "岑彭"
      ],
      "text": "臣不敢，特地前来接驾。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00021",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王莽"
      ],
      "text": "想当初甲子之年曾开科场，你与马武二人技艺相同，那时孤家中了你的相貌，不中马武的才能，不想他一怒，就在长安城外题下反诗，蛊惑黎民，险些成了大事。你不知以恩报德，反降他人，你的天良何在？",
      "text_length": 91
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00022",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "王莽"
      ],
      "text": "小岑彭你不必巧言遮盖，曾记得甲子年把科场来开。中了你相貌好，格外优待，弃了那马子章栋梁之才。又谁知到如今良心改坏，你竟敢放大胆来到云台。",
      "text_length": 68
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00023",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王莽"
      ],
      "text": "你是何人？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00024",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "邳彤"
      ],
      "text": "臣邳彤前来接驾。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00025",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王莽"
      ],
      "text": "邳彤，怎么你也降顺刘秀了？我且问你，大元帅他往哪里去了？",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00026",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "邳彤"
      ],
      "text": "大元帅他战死疆场了。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00027",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王莽"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，不好了！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00028",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "王莽"
      ],
      "text": "听说是战死了大元帅，我心中好一似刀来裁。眼前若有苏献在，哪怕那汉兵将到此来。",
      "text_length": 38
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00029",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马武"
      ],
      "text": "姚仁兄，你看他三人俱作过王莽的臣子，断断不能动手捉拿于他，待我二人进观将他拿下便了。",
      "text_length": 42
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00030",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王莽"
      ],
      "text": "外面二人是谁？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00031",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜茂",
        "岑彭",
        "邳彤"
      ],
      "text": "乃是姚期、马武二人。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00032",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王莽"
      ],
      "text": "你待怎讲？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00033",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜茂",
        "岑彭",
        "邳彤"
      ],
      "text": "姚期、马武二人。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00034",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王莽"
      ],
      "text": "此二人乃是孤家冤家对头，今日到来，我命休矣！",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00035",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "王莽"
      ],
      "text": "听说是姚期、马子章，倒叫孤家无主张。他二人与孤家夙有冤枉，看起来我性命休定丧无常。",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00036",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "马武",
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "待我等打进去！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00037",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "马武、姚期同拿王莽，同下，杜茂、岑彭、邳彤同下。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00038",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四龙套、四太监、刘秀、邓禹同上。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00039",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "云台观内捉王莽，且听探马报端详。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00040",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "探马上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00041",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "探马"
      ],
      "text": "启主公：王莽拿到。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00042",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "将王莽绑至法场。来，带马。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00043",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "刘秀、邓禹、四龙套、四太监同大转场。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00044",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "将王莽押上来。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00045",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四龙套"
      ],
      "text": "将王莽押上来。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00046",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "内西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "王莽"
      ],
      "text": "八月十五把寿拜，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00047",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四刀手押王莽同上。姚期、马武、杜茂、岑彭、邳彤同上。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00048",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮二六板",
      "speakers": [
        "王莽"
      ],
      "text": "满朝中的文武拜金阶。三杯药酒把平帝爷害，稳坐龙台称孤的心怀。实指望汉家绝了后代，以谁知白水村出了个妖人刘秀，又报仇来。而如今身捆铁索法场外，事到临头我悔也悔不来。",
      "text_length": 81
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00049",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王莽"
      ],
      "text": "吓，御外男，愚外公这厢有礼了。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00050",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "来，看酒祭奠。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00051",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖吹打〗。刘秀、杜茂、岑彭、邳彤同行礼，邓禹、姚期、马武同站。",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00052",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王莽"
      ],
      "text": "吓，御外男，这千不是万不是乃是孤一时的糊涂，虽然作了一十八载的江山，并不曾残害过刘氏子孙。今日你已身登大宝，纵然将孤杀死，于你又有何益？望祈你念这甥舅之亲，将我饶恕，放我一条老命，孤就在这云台观内悟道参禅，修真养性，不修今生，我还要修修来世。话已讲明，这杀也在你，不杀也在你吓。",
      "text_length": 139
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014018_e00053",
      "play_id": "01014018",
      "scene_id": "01014018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "你看王莽在此苦苦哀求，泪如泉涌，小王意欲念在甥舅亲情，赦他一条性命，不知列位意下如何？",
      "text_length": 43
    },
    {
